---item_138 Stationary Sniper---
Type :: Gun
Slot :: Gun
Gun Definition :: [[Stationary Sniper]]
Rarity :: Exotic
Durability :: 5

Creates a targeting zone with first bullet of every magazine. Shots fired while standing in your own zone deal significantly more damage.

The best hunters know when to roam and when to claim their territory.

